<br>
Although i dont know alot about other enchanters on the server, i do often hear war stories. I have also talked to several other folks, enchanters, and it makes me hysterical.<br>
<br>
Since we are talking about enchanters, i spose ill talk to some enchanters first.<br>
<br>
I know everyone knows this, but let me tell you anyway ;). I see these as facts.<br>
<br>
1) Your mezzes are fixed duration. Thats right!! No guessing, they are timed!!<br>
<br>
2) HP is very important, sacrifice some items acourdingly for hp. I see so many enchanters with 60k in the bank, at level 60, with 1200-1400 hp!! Whats that all about. If you have NEVER been guilded and NEVER attended a raid, you can reach the 16--, 1700 level of hp with minimal trade offs to stats. Its all about every second you can live. You KNOW you will receaive aggro multiple times during grind groups, no matter who tanks. Resists will get you owned quick, if you have no hp, your group dies, your a shitty enchanter, etc etc etc. Tanks need time to grab aggro, every second you live adds to the overall success of your group.<br>
<br>
3) Rapture is your friend!! When your in a group, always use your highest level of mezz first, then overwrite it with a lower line which can be resisted easier. A lesser mezz will overwrite a higher, keeping you alive. Im 63 atm, so i dont know the other newer mezzez well, and cant speak of them. If you can use a rapture, use it, then follow up with a dazzle (pre PoP). A mezz can also be used as a form of stun if you will, in emergencies when you dont have a stun loaded.<br>
<br>
4) You ARE a buffing class. Yes it sucks, deal with it. Tanks want VoG, give it to them, they want shissar, SoV, whatever, hook it up. Its not like we burn all that much mana in a smooth, effective group. Its what we do, dont bitch about saving a lil mana.<br>
<br>
5) Group in tough zones. It keeps you sharp, and its fun!! I know ae is easy exp, but sometinmes you have to just group. FYI-If you ae now after PoP im amazed. PoP exp is amazing.<br>
<br>
6) Pets still break mezz. This is fact. Yes they patched it, it doesnt happen as often, but i have news for you. It still happens. Its a pain in the ass when other pets, or yours break mez. If a mob is mezzed, and you try to attack with pet, it prolly wont. The catch is, it depends on when you land the mez if a mob is fighting. If its between rounds or some weird tweak, it will attack trough your mezz, breaking it. <br>
<br>
7) Never, ever, ever, ever, sell a c3. Im not gonna lie, i used to sell the hell outta c3, just because you will get paid. Let me tell you, the tells i receive while role are amazing. No i will not sell you a c3. If i dont know you, im not even answering you. Im sorry, im not tryin to be a dick, but shit its just overwhelming. If you sell c3, you will get yours eventually. Hey, better you than me.<br>
<br>
*pauses a moment to watch christina aguilera dirty video*<br>
<br>
Here is some opinion.<br>
<br>
1) Its my opinion charisma blows. I didnt use pets before dire charm. They will own you quick.  I Will say dire charm IS finally great in PoP. I can deal damage!! Its fucking amazing!!! If you dont have DC in the planes in some situations your cheating yourself and the group. When fighting some 63's, any damage helps to keep you grinding. 70-80 dps isnt bad. <br>
<br>
2) HP is important!!<br>
<br>
3) When your getting wailed on, stand there and take it, and spam your roots/mezz/slows on it. Slow is last case scenerio due to cast time. Sometimes its needed though. Running around like a goon wont help you one damn bit.<br>
<br>
Other classes.<br>
<br>
1) when your getting wailed on, stand there and take it so chanter doesnt have to follow you around, targeting is a bitch at times. make aggro known if not, and stand there or do your thing, just dont run arounfd like a damn fool.<br>
<br>
2) For those who pull 4-5 mobs. Ok np, now as i call mezz, back up 10 feet. This makes targeting sooooo much easier. Please for the love of Jesus (tm). if at all possible, just step back a bit.<br>
<br>
3) Watch you pets!!!<br>
<br>
4) Clerics dont slack off!!<br>
<br>
5) thank you to tanks who use the shieled command. Well, i really only group with a few tanks, but thank you!!! (bapz!!). Any damage not going to the chanter is more TIME. Time being the key factor to success or a pain in the ass CR.<br>
<br>
<br>
With the release of PoP, things have changed. There is a reason we get a 1500 hp free rune. Its cause these bastards will kick your ass, and fast. PoP makes old world, even luclin, pale in comparison. I fell like a level 20 chanter again. Ill admit, shit was to easy, and exp sucked. Now, the risk is much much greater, the reward greater, and the bordom level low. <br>
<br>
I feel the planes have once again brought fun to a old ass class.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
