<br>
Perhaps you don't understand that enchanter have no control over there own pets.  No back off command.  Nothing, unless you get the AA skill they are selling.  Now given that pet CAN break mezz.  You the chanter try to mezz and add it resists, mob hits you, pet attacks, you stun (if it is stunnable), remezz, PET BREAKS MEZZ.  Not good for a piece of crap pet.  The mobs is still pounding on you, no need to try to remezz again because you will be dead first.  Other pet classes can back there pets off.<br>
